Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.70,0:01:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十二話\N少年劍客誕生！\N首席弟子禰彥的戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.63,0:02:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對！劍心不是這樣做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.54,0:02:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是這樣吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.24,0:02:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這…這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.71,0:02:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是我的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.85,0:02:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斷掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.08,0:02:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.55,0:03:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夾腳…斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.91,0:03:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,修好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.78,0:03:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思 修得不怎麼好看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.65,0:03:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…不會啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.02,0:03:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油啊！好好練劍！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.01,0:03:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕！忘了謝謝她了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.60,0:04:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從剛剛就一直沒動筷子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.21,0:04:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？你到底怎麼啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.71,0:04:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩！該不會是交女朋友了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.92,0:04:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才…才沒有呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.42,0:04:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茶端來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.03,0:04:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊!小燕姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.37,0:05:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你！小燕！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.11,0:05:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒見過嗎？這是小燕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.38,0:05:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩…恩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.68,0:05:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她上禮拜開始在我店堸筐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.45,0:05:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我最喜歡小燕姐姐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.02,0:05:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們再一起玩手球喔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.69,0:05:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.36,0:05:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小燕 麻煩去提桶水來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.33,0:05:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.86,0:05:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她真是個能幹的好孩子\N店堛漱H都很喜歡她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.00,0:05:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有句話忘了說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.30,0:05:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.24,0:05:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.78,0:05:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.05,0:05:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.39,0:05:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛剛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.42,0:05:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.39,0:05:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.20,0:06:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.60,0:06:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就說嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.04,0:06:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才要謝你呢！你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.15,0:06:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！我叫明神禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.48,0:06:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明神…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.35,0:06:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你！禰彥弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.46,0:06:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥…弟弟？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.87,0:06:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看起來有那麼小嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.84,0:06:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！小燕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.78,0:06:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像做得不錯嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.71,0:06:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該已順利取得店堳H任了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.22,0:06:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點！過來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.10,0:07:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唉！怎麼啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.94,0:07:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在問你怎麼啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.04,0:07:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,店堥癡S有放什麼錢\N每天賺的錢老闆都拿回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.48,0:07:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼！不要自作聰明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.18,0:07:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鑄模應該順利拿到了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.09,0:07:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是說店老闆家的鑰匙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.29,0:07:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是叫你用粘土采型嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.46,0:07:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是不要這麼做的好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.76,0:07:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干雄大人你原來是旗本\N當盜賊有傷旗本名聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.40,0:07:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼時候輪到你對我說教啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.74,0:07:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我家在江戶三百年來\N一直是你家的主子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.31,0:07:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連你父親都對我唯命是從
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.82,0:08:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是當強盜還是不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.22,0:08:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有義務照我的命令行事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.12,0:08:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼！拿不到鑰匙\N我就殺了你老闆全家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.26,0:08:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.50,0:08:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰？人在哪堙H
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.40,0:08:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明治都過了十年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.44,0:08:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還用江戶時代 主從關係相要脅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.31,0:08:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知你們原來是否旗本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.38,0:08:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同為士族的我\N絕不容許你們為非做歹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.41,0:08:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.78,0:08:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰…禰彥弟弟！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.22,0:08:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託不要再叫我弟弟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.65,0:08:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.60,0:08:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥弟弟！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.54,0:08:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要叫我弟弟！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.34,0:08:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對…對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.91,0:09:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最好放棄當強盜的蠢念頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.51,0:09:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否則東京士族\N明神禰彥就和你們卯上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.85,0:09:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不知死活！給我上！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.49,0:09:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這小鬼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.77,0:09:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管用了！劍術派上用場了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.41,0:09:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每天苦練終於有成果了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.04,0:09:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真討厭！這下非得感謝阿薰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.98,0:09:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.29,0:09:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁現在！打死這小鬼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.13,0:09:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手！住手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.07,0:10:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.44,0:10:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在幹什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.14,0:10:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他可是重要的首席弟子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.71,0:10:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.71,0:10:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不是說好靜觀其變嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.62,0:10:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果現在幫他的話\N怎樣也成不了氣候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.39,0:10:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且這場戰鬥\N禰彥打算用自己的力量打贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.10,0:10:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手！住手！求求你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.51,0:10:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手！拜託你們住手！\N干雄大人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.74,0:10:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟他無關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.28,0:10:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我交出鑄模就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.21,0:10:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿嘿！喂！差不多可以停手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.28,0:10:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵命！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.45,0:10:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以後要照我說的話做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.46,0:10:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少管閒事 禰彥弟弟！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.20,0:11:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…還好吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.67,0:11:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡！一對一的話\N我決不會輸你們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.17,0:11:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起！把你拖下水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.44,0:11:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.81,0:11:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們什麼時候下手？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.38,0:11:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！明天晚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.68,0:11:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定要阻止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.39,0:11:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥弟弟 啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.82,0:11:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.16,0:11:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果連那幫人都阻止不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.06,0:11:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就真的是弟弟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.33,0:11:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是你拖我下水\N是我自己要做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.97,0:11:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以你不要自責
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.07,0:11:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這事不能報警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.77,0:11:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,報了警這女孩就成了共犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.34,0:11:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那幫人這種三腳貓\N決不可麻煩劍心他們出面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.08,0:11:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我一個人的戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.96,0:12:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要怎麼做才打得贏呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.53,0:12:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們人那麼多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.44,0:12:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.08,0:12:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以坐下嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.61,0:12:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩！啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.29,0:13:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直在想新的練功方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.42,0:13:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能不能教我\N一個人要怎麼打好幾個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.80,0:13:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.70,0:13:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你遇到這種情況了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.97,0:13:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有啦！我只是隨口問問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.67,0:13:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣啊！只有一種方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.27,0:13:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的有嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.14,0:13:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幕府末期維新武士們\N以寡敵眾所用的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.25,0:13:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先就是逃跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.88,0:13:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逃跑？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.82,0:13:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人當然會緊追不捨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.45,0:13:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣就會有人落單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.02,0:13:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跑得快的人會追上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.99,0:13:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就各個擊倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.56,0:13:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再繼續跑 重複運用即可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.43,0:13:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.03,0:13:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是要用這方法\N腳力好是絕對不可或缺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.84,0:13:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,腳力？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.84,0:13:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先要確定對方有多少人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.38,0:14:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如何才能維持一對一的情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.18,0:14:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一對一…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.79,0:14:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有 禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.33,0:14:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神谷活心派用的是活人劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.86,0:14:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是保護人的劍
